    "title": "Motivation",
    "description": "&quot;You only see the light you shine.&quot; The mechanisms at play in this process are projection, reflection, interpretation, and experimentation. How much suffering received is naught but suffering exuded? \n\nWhen you look at the drawing under red light (or while considering the first chakra), the red text becomes invisible. Now the message reads &quot;only the light you shine&quot; -- a much deeper statement. We actively create the whole universe, beyond just playing an active role in the creation of our interpretation of the local universe.  \n",
